"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/824745","Cabinet Office","false","2018-03-29","<p>A copy of the letter indemnifying the Official Receiver was placed in both House on 15<sup>th</sup> January 2018.</p><p> </p>","Hertsmere","Oliver Dowden",,"2018-03-29T10:10:58.423Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/824745/answer","Biography information for Oliver Dowden","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/824745/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/824745/answer",,,,,"53","Cabinet Office","Cabinet Office","2018-01-17","Carillion: Insolvency","1","House of Commons","To ask the Minister for the Cabinet Office, pursuant to the Oral Statement of 15 January, Official Report, Column  624 on Carillon, if he will publish the indemnity given to the Official Receiver.","false","Biography information for Chi Onwurah","Newcastle upon Tyne Central","Chi Onwurah","123546"
